    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>
      BeachBride is provided "as is." We are not liable for any damages arising from your use of the site or reliance on its content, including vendor interactions, travel disruptions, or inaccurate regulatory information.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
